3. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  SynthesisStageExecutor:  executeStage(stageName, candidate, outputType [, priorStageOutputs]); buildContext from FlowCandidate (flowName, flowType, services, steps, codeEvidence, logPatterns, graphContext, complexity); retrieveAdditionalContext returns Map.of(); generateWithRetry (maxRetries 2, template "synthesis-" + stageName).
  FlowAnalysisStage:       analyze(candidate) → executor.executeStage("stage1", ...), minio.putJson evidence/synthesis/stage1/{snapshotId}/{candidateId}.json
  CodeExplanationStage:    explain(candidate, flowAnalysis) → priorStageOutput = serialize(flowAnalysis), executor.executeStage("stage2", ...), minio.putJson stage2
  RiskAssessmentStage:     assess(candidate, flowAnalysis, codeExplanation) → flowAnalysis + codeExplanation serialized, executor.executeStage("stage3", ...), minio.putJson stage3
  SynthesisStages1To3Service:  runStages1To3(candidate) — sequential stage1 → stage2 → stage3 with latency timers (flowforge.synthesis.stage1/2/3.latency); runAllCandidates(candidates) — Executors.newVirtualThreadPerTaskExecutor(), submit per candidate, filter null on exception.

